### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{login.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### Listar Usuários (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Listar Usuários por Role (GOV)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10&role=GOV
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Listar Usuários por Role (USER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10&role=USER
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Listar Usuários Comuns (Vítimas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10&type=COMMON
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Listar Usuários do Sistema (Agentes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10&type=SYSTEM
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

